cement</span></div><h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl font-serif font-light tracking-tight text-white mb-2 leading-none">KAWE.com</h1></div><div class="space-y-4"><p class="text-lg md:text-xl font-serif text-[#888] leading-relaxed border-l border-white/10 pl-5">KAWE.com captures the Maori verb meaning to carry, convey, and transport, a foundational concept in logistics and cultural transmission.</p><p class="text-lg md:text-xl font-serif text-[#888] leading-relaxed border-l border-white/10 pl-5">The global logistics and transportation market exceeds $10 trillion. Identifiers with authentic Pacific Island linguistic provenance carry unique cultural positioning.</p><p class="text-lg md:text-xl font-serif text-[#888] leading-relaxed border-l border-white/10 pl-5">Four-letter .com domains with genuine Polynesian meaning serve as distinctive anchors for logistics and cultural platforms.</p></div><div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 pt-6 border-t border-white/5"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-shield-check w-4 h-4 text-[#555] shrink-0 mt-0.5" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z"></path><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"></path></svg><div><p class="text-[11px] font-mono text-white tracking-[0.1em] mb-0.5 uppercase">Secure Settlement</p><p class="text-xs text-[#666] leading-relaxed">Cleared via Escrow.com.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-bitcoin w-4 h-4 text-[#555] shrink-0 mt-0.5" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M11.767 19.089c4.924.868 6.14-6.025 1.216-6.894m-1.216 6.894L5.86 18.047m5.908 1.042-.347 1.97m1.563-8.864c4.924.869 6.14-6.025 1.215-6.893m-1.215 6.893-3.94-.694m5.155-6.2L8.29 4.26m5.908 1.042.348-1.97M7.48 20.364l3.126-17.727"></path></svg><div><p class="text-[11px] font-mono text-white tracking-[0.1em] mb-0.5 uppercase">Crypto Accepted</p><p class="text-xs text-[#666] leading-relaxed">Stablecoins, BTC, and ETH.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="lg:col-span-5 relative"><div class="bg-[#050505] rounded-none p-8 md:p-10 border border-white/10 relative overflow-hidden"><div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-white/20 to-transparent"></div><h3 class="text-[10px] font-mono tracking-[0.4em] text-[#666] uppercase mb-6 border-b border-white/5 pb-4">Acquisition Protocol</h3><div class="space-y-2 mb-8"><p class="text-[11px] font-mono text-[#888] uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">Asset Status</p><p class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-serif text-white tracking-tight">Accepting Offers</p></div><button class="group relative flex items-center justify-between bg-white hover:bg-[#e0e0e0] text-black w-full py-4 px-6 font-mono tracking-[0.2em] font-bold text-[11px] transition-all uppercase"><span>Make an Offer</span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-arrow-right w-4 h-4 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"></path></svg></button><div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 text-[9px] font-mono tracking-[0.1em] text-[#555] uppercase pt-6"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-lock w-3 h-3" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="18" height